Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:10.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Cease what you are\Ndoing and gaze at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:14.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop everything, save for\Nthe thrumming of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:17.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Theft. It is an\Nespecially sweet vice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:19.21,Main,,0,0,0,,more elegant than vandalism
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:21.42,Main,,0,0,0,,and more complex\Nthan simple robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,A beautiful blend of secrets\Nand crime and mischief and fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.43,0:00:27.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Like dear Heathcliff,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:30.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I am defined by my\Nall-consuming passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:33.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Stealing is my greatest\Ncarnal pleasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,a pleasure for which\NI will risk my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:38.34,Main,,0,0,0,,a sexy prison from\Nwhich there is no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:41.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Why am I this way?\NWho can know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.36,0:00:44.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is the slave and\Nwho's the master?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:47.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Do divine eyes fall\Nupon me any longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,or have the given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:51.40,Main,,0,0,0,,The rush of a theft\Nallows me to forget all,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:55.20,Main,,0,0,0,,and yet to distantly\Nremember all, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:03.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Run and speak not.\NHide and run not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:05.35,Main,,0,0,0,,When you've found\Nme, punish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:09.32,Main,,0,0,0,,When you've punished\Nme, kill me. Save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Little boy, there is nothing\Nleft to steal from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:21.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You have long been an\Nempty shell. Just as I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:25.21,Main,,0,0,0,,And so, if you would gaze at\Nme, cease what you are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:29.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop everything save for the\Nthrumming of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:42.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we have a picture, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:46.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, "Geisha!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:48.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, "pretty geisha!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:57.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:01:58.34,Main,,0,0,0,,A miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:01.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:03.38,Main,,0,0,0,,A blind man could tell\NI made that shot dead-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:07.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to win, you got to\Nhit exactly the right spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:10.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss by even a little bit,\Nand there's no joy for anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:11.29,Main,,0,0,0,,mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:12.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:14.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You win some, you lose some.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:15.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm curious, Jigen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:18.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What was it that made you\Naccept my invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:19.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:22.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm homeless and I'm broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:26.20,Main,,0,0,0,,A job that came with a spa\Nvacation sounded pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:29.24,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what made you\Ninvite me along?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:31.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Handling perishable\Nmerchandise on your own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:32.33,Main,,0,0,0,,is a tricky business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:34.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to\Nkeep things fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.29,Main,,0,0,0,,It's about time we got started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:41.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for playing, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll just take\Nthis one, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:04.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, step right\Nup and take a closer look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.28,Main,,0,0,0,,No charge until\Nthe show's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:10.36,Main,,0,0,0,,The most frightening event of\Nthe evening is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:12.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you hear those noises?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:14.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Those are the moans\Nof the Snake Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:16.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, come on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:24.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Disturbing, yet fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.33,Main,,0,0,0,,How can you look away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,She is but one exhibit in\Nour museum of living art,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:32.33,Main,,0,0,0,,a mere prelude to the\Nnight's main attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.34,Main,,0,0,0,,It starts to get a\Nlittle difficult around
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:38.22,Main,,0,0,0,,the fifteenth time or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:40.41,Main,,0,0,0,,And finally, we are proud\Nto be showcasing the work
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:44.28,Main,,0,0,0,,of the last artistic genius\Nof the twentieth century:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:45.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Aiden Nartar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,The great master\Nof magical realism.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourselves for\Nthe truly incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:59.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Said to be the fruit of an\Nunholy union between human
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:02.20,Main,,0,0,0,,and beast deep in heart\Nof the Amazon Jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.26,Main,,0,0,0,,These patterns were\Ntattooed on her body
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:07.35,Main,,0,0,0,,shortly after her birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:15.22,Main,,0,0,0,,For the sins of the parents,\Nthe child must pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:19.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Turn your gaze and look upon the\NKaleidoscope Woman, if you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:40.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:43.30,Main,,0,0,0,,This woman's body became\NAiden Nartar's canvas
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,when she was still an infant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:47.37,Main,,0,0,0,,She is a living painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:50.32,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a once in\Na lifetime opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Never again will you see\Na woman so valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Take a moment, ladies and\Ngentlemen, and consider
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:59.21,Main,,0,0,0,,the worth of such a prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:06.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Bidding starts at\None million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.35,Main,,0,0,0,,One and a half million!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Do we have two million?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:11.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Three million!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Three and half million!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:13.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Four million!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I bid four point two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Four point three million!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:16.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Four and a half!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Four point eight million!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:19.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:21.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:26.37,Main,,0,0,0,,That was too soon, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:27.43,Main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You see what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:43.30,Main,,0,0,0,,That game was rigged--my shots\Nalways hit dead-center.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,That's far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:01.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop running, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:26.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a pretty\Nfoxy lady up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.34,Main,,0,0,0,,This poor kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:41.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She's even got 'em\Non her tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:49.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking she\Ncan't talk, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.35,Main,,0,0,0,,She's a piece of art:\Na living, breathing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:58.43,Main,,0,0,0,,ever-shifting canvas designed\Nfor the viewer's enjoyment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:01.26,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the idea, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:04.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Her creator would have treated\Nher like any other painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,And why would anyone\Nwaste time trying to teach
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:08.32,Main,,0,0,0,,a painting how to speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:12.33,Main,,0,0,0,,This artist is a\Nseriously twisted guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:16.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Turning her entire life\Ninto some grotesque exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Easy, Casanova.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't have the loot\Ngetting a crush on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.25,Main,,0,0,0,,That would just be awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm just bein' nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Hand over the goods, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:58.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I figured it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Great. Her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Give me the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:03.30,Main,,0,0,0,,She belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:06.32,Main,,0,0,0,,You know I've got\Na soft spot for fine ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Now that I know she's\Nsuch a fox, I can't just
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:11.23,Main,,0,0,0,,turn her over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.40,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:14.29,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll do this the hard way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:15.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:19.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Stay close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it just me, or does she\Nseem a lot more wound up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:29.23,Main,,0,0,0,,than usual today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:30.37,Main,,0,0,0,,That time of the month, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:35.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Eeny, meany, miny, moe,\Ncatch a geisha by the toe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:36.43,Main,,0,0,0,,If she--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Hollers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:39.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Catch you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:05.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Fujiko,\Nis there anything you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:08.24,Main,,0,0,0,,And now, viewers, we have a\Ndisplay of rare treasures
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:09.40,Main,,0,0,0,,from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:12.33,Main,,0,0,0,,First up, we have a\Nsolid-gold teapot studded
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:14.30,Main,,0,0,0,,with three-carat diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:17.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Next, a durian--the\Nking of fruits!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.38,Main,,0,0,0,,This fine specimen is one\Nof the largest ever recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:23.35,Main,,0,0,0,,And, finally, the\Nmasterpiece of the century!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:27.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Not too hard on\Nthe eyes, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:28.38,Main,,0,0,0,,This is truly incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:31.22,Main,,0,0,0,,A work of art with\Nits own biography.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:35.28,Main,,0,0,0,,A painting with a riveting tale,\Nthe tale called life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:40.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You can find her in the circus\Ntent at Hatami Hot Springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Fujiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:55.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:56.42,Main,,0,0,0,,One way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I will make it mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Careful, it's a long way down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:14.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Is she trying to kill us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.30,Main,,0,0,0,,She's barely aiming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:32.20,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like she doesn't even\Ncare if the loot gets damaged
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.39,Main,,0,0,0,,in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:56.28,Main,,0,0,0,,This is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:09.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:12.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I think she's finally lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like she's possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:34.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Time to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.22,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:37.30,Main,,0,0,0,,From this height it's suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:43.43,Main,,0,0,0,,One, Two, Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:45.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:12:59.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Think she's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:15.31,Main,,0,0,0,,If she dies in a place like\Nthis, she's not the woman
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:17.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:48.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujiko's not the only one\Nwith a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:52.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Lupin's hiding something, too,\Nthe dirty, scheming bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:01.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:04.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Happiness doesn't come\Neasy with so much baggage
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:07.41,Main,,0,0,0,,to carry around\Nbut--Try anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:10.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Just do your best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:27.21,Main,,0,0,0,,The only description we\Nhave is "painted lady."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You think we're gonna\Nrecognize her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:32.32,Main,,0,0,0,,From what I hear, she's worth\Nquite a pretty penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:34.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I just hope there aren't\Nany big-time crooks
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:35.35,Main,,0,0,0,,looking for her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:56.38,Main,,0,0,0,,What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:58.38,Main,,0,0,0,,But did it actually kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:21.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Pretty amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:23.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Man, I wish I'd brought\Na camera with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:25.35,Main,,0,0,0,,That would sure give\Nthe wife a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.41,Main,,0,0,0,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,They're trying to\Nrun us off the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:53.42,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell\Nare they after?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:30.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:49.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I got ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:53.25,Main,,0,0,0,,It's time to go-go-go-go-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:55.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:57.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:10.34,Main,,0,0,0,,A-ba ba ba ba-ba,\Na-ba ba ba ba ba ba ba
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:12.26,Main,,0,0,0,,The water feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:14.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come on in\Nand join us, Fujiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:20.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Toodle-oodle-oo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:35.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You better be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:37.35,Main,,0,0,0,,It gets really hot at\Nthe source of the spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:53.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Judges give it\Na ten point oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You've hit a dead-end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:18.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:22.41,Main,,0,0,0,,We're surrounded by extremely\Nvolatile natural gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,One spark from this baby\Nand we're all crispy critters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:30.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What do want from\Nthis lady, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:30.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:31.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:33.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do I steal anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:35.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I can sell her to the highest\Nbidder for a ton of ca--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:38.37,Main,,0,0,0,,If that was your game, you'd\Nwant her in pristine condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:40.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't want to scratch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:43.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Any damage tanks the\Nprice and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.37,Main,,0,0,0,,So what are you\Nreally after, Fujiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to kill\Nthe poor girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.26,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:56.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It's yourself\Nyou want to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:59.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Your life's been\Nmanipulated by strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:05.29,Main,,0,0,0,,When you steal, when you eat,\Neven when you breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:08.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything you do is part\Nof somebody else's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:15.23,Main,,0,0,0,,People you don't even know\Nthrew your destiny off-course,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:20.40,Main,,0,0,0,,but you have to go on living;\Npowerless and pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:24.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You see yourself when you look\Nat her, and you can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:27.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Fujiko Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:31.28,Main,,0,0,0,,And if it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:32.39,Main,,0,0,0,,What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:36.34,Main,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:39.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm\Nthe best one to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:11.20,Main,,0,0,0,,That's actually a squirt gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:12.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't take\Nanother step, Fujiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:24.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Shoot, and you blow us all up,\Njust so ya know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:26.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:27.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you know\Nabout that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:33.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm not letting\Nthat cat out of the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:35.43,Main,,0,0,0,,My life's a lot more fun,\Nthanks to Fujiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:39.25,Main,,0,0,0,,And that's not something\NI'm willing to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:57.20,Main,,0,0,0,,So much for the\Nliving painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:59.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I think she deserves\Na blank canvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:14.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell,\Nwhat the hell, what the hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:21.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell,\Nwhat the hell, wha--.
